---
title: Spiced Lentil Cottage Pie with Garlic Greens
description: With juicy currants that burst in your mouth with every bite, there’s a lot more under the fluffy mashed potato surface of this pie than meets the eye…
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b72617330006c696358a5c2-580e4e71.jpg
